ber-encryption/src/lib.rs` | `b\"reme-receipt-v1:\"` | `b\"ember-receipt-v1:\"` | Domain sep |\n| `crates/ember-encryption/src/lib.rs` | `b\"reme-identity-v1:\"` | `b\"ember-identity-v1:\"` | Domain sep |\n| `crates/ember-message/src/lib.rs` | `b\"reme-content-id-v1\"` | `b\"ember-content-id-v1\"` | Content ID |\n| `crates/ember-message/src/tombstone.rs` | `\"reme-ack-hash-v1\"` | `\"ember-ack-hash-v1\"` | KDF context |\n| `crates/ember-identity/src/encrypted.rs` | `b\"reme-identity-v1\"` (16 bytes) | `b\"embr-identity-v1\"` (16 bytes) | Must stay 16 bytes |\n| `crates/ember-bundle/src/lib.rs` | `b\"REME\"` (4 bytes) | `b\"EMBR\"` (4 bytes) | Must stay 4 bytes |\n\n### Step 5: Config / environment / binary names\n\n| File(s) | Change |\n|---|---|\n| `apps/client/src/config.rs` | All `REME_*` env vars -> `EMBER_*`, `\"reme\"` binary name -> `\"ember\"`, `ProjectDirs::from(\"com\", \"branch\", \"reme\")` -> `ProjectDirs::from(\"chat\", \"getember\", \"ember\")`, `identity.reme` -> `identity.ember` |\n| `apps/node/src/config.rs` | All `REME_NODE_*` env vars -> `EMBER_NODE_*`, `\"reme-node\"` binary name -> `\"ember-node\"`, `ProjectDirs::from(...)` update, `\"reme/v1\"` MQTT topic -> `\"ember/v1\"` |\n| `apps/client/src/tui/mod.rs` | `\"identity.reme\"` -> `\"identity.ember\"` |\n| `apps/client/src/import.rs` | `\"identity.reme\"` -> `\"identity.ember\"` |\n| `apps/client/src/export.rs` | `.reme` extension -> `.ember` in tests |\n\n### Step 6: Transport protocol identifiers\n\n| File | Change |\n|---|---|\n| `crates/ember-transport/src/mqtt.rs` | `DEFAULT_TOPIC_PREFIX = \"reme/v1\"` -> `\"ember/v1\"`, client ID prefix `\"reme-\"` -> `\"ember-\"` |\n| `crates/ember-transport/src/mqtt_receiver.rs` | Same topic prefix + client ID |\n| `crates/ember-transport/src/mqtt_target.rs` | Same topic prefix + client ID |\n| `crates/ember-transport/src/http_target.rs` | `\"application/vnd.reme.bundle\"` -> `\"application/vnd.ember.bundle\"` |\n| `crates/ember-transport/src/http.rs` 